---
By: Henry Drummond
Locus:
  Page: 307
  Verse: 9
Tags:
  - ''
---
Instead of allowing yourself to be unhappy, just let your love grow as God
wants it to grow. Seek goodness in others. Love more persons more. Love
them more impersonally, more unselfishly, without thought of return. The
return, never fear, will take care of itself.
